obj_root_law:
  slug the-central-goods-and-services-tax-act-2017
  handle (15689)
  collectionHandle 123456789/1362
  title `The Central Goods and Services Tax Act, 2017`
  actNumber (12)
  enactmentDate 2017-04-12
  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/15689`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  hindiTitle `केंद्रीयमालऔरसेवाकरअधिनियम, 2017`
  actYear (2017)
  ministry `Ministry of Finance`
  department `Department of Revenue`
  longTitle `An Act to make a provision for levy and collection of tax on intra-State supply of goods or services or both by the Central Government and for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`
  enforcementDate `22nd June, 2017 for sections 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 10, 22, 23, 24, 25, 26, 27, 28, 29, 30, 139, 146 and 164 1st July, 2017 for sections 6 to 9, 11 to 21, 31 to 41, 42 (except proviso to sub-section (9) of S 42), 43 (except proviso to subsection (9) of S 43), 44 to 50, 53 to 138, 140 to 163, 165 to 174.`
  notification `22nd June, 2017 vide notification No. G.S.R. 605 (E) dated the 19th June, 2017, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3(i) for sections 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 10, 22, 23, 24, 25, 26, 27, 28, 29, 30, 139, 146 and 164. 1st July, 2017 vide notification No. G.S.R 658 (E) dated 28th June, 2017, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3(i) for sections 6 to 9, 11 to 21, 31 to 41, 42 (except proviso to sub-section (9) of S 42), 43 (except proviso to subsection (9) of S 43), 44 to 50, 53 to 138, 140 to 163, 165 to 174.`
  fetchedAt `2026-05-09T15:38:09.082Z`
  translations obj_root_law_translations
