  orderNo 46
  title Omitted.
  content `43A. [Procedure for furnishing return and availing input tax credit].--- Omitted by the Finance Act, 2022 (6 of 2022), s. 107 (w.e.f. 1-10-2022).`
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_43_a_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_2_00042_201712_1517807328102&sectionId=51462&sectionno=43A&orderno=46&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_2_00042_201712_1517807328102
